菌。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n所以普通感冒唔睇都冇所謂，想要拎假都係睇平啲好。"},{"pid":"fa1479c10bf1c2f6445329e6718daacf0746bdac","tid":2056824,"uid":42548,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T03:33:51.000Z","msg":"唔係百五蚊咩？？"},{"pid":"de425c0b4e5b9a243c7aceee57754ef2f07b0e7b","tid":2056824,"uid":36494,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"dbf22144dc53f74df4067c1f4758bd2ccd6bfbd2","tid":2056824,"uid":50878,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T03:24:18.000Z","msg":"不嬲睇開都800 至1000蚊起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3舊水真心信唔過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 剩係診金都唔止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T04:01:00.000Z","msg":"Rich"},{"pid":"91816f300c038128bc6ec0803ff3cab2778ec747","tid":2056824,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbf22144dc53f74df4067c1f4758bd2ccd6bfbd2","tid":2056824,"uid":50878,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T03:24:18.000Z","msg":"不嬲睇開都800 至1000蚊起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3舊水真心信唔過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 剩係診金都唔止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T04:01:54.000Z","msg":"傷風感冒睇咁貴如果你無保險包我唔知應該話你錢多定咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6831ece82450523c2f6bea8c388f68183d6be6e","tid":2056824,"uid":50878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"91816f300c038128bc6ec0803ff3cab2778ec747","tid":2056824,"uid":39710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbf22144dc53f74df4067c1f4758bd2ccd6bfbd2","tid":2056824,"uid":50878,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-09T03:24:18.000Z","msg":"不嬲睇開都800 至1000蚊起<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3舊水真心信唔過<img src=\